# Apify Replacement — copy to `.env` and fill in. Never commit your real `.env`.
# Every value below is a placeholder; nothing here ties to any account.

YELP_API_KEY=   # Optional — Yelp Fusion free tier (5000/day) for business discovery. Leave blank to skip.
BROWSERBASE_API_KEY=   # Optional — residential-IP proxy for high-volume social scraping. Leave blank to run direct.
